text: Horaglanis alikunhii is a species of airbreathing catfish endemic to India. It was described by Subhash Babu Kallikadavil and Nayar in 2004.Horaglanis alikunhii in FishBase ==References== Category:Horaglanis Category:Catfish of Asia Category:Cave fish Category:Freshwater fish of India Category:Fish described in 2004
